_refine.details                                  
;Refinement involved replacing the peptide in 1OXN 
and adjusting side chains and waters.
The discrepancies between observed reflections and 
reflections used for refinement is due to merging of 
Bijvoet mates during refinement. Since the dataset
was collected at the zinc anomalous edge, the Bijvoet 
mates are not identical and represent crystallographically 
unique reflections.
;
